      </div>
      
      <div class="ban-category">
        <h3>1. Categorically Excluded Cards</h3>
        <p>The following cards are banned from the 50-card deck (and command zone):</p>
        <ul class="category-list">
          <li>Silver-bordered, Gold-bordered, or Acorn-stamped cards</li>
          <li>Cards with the card type Conspiracy</li>
          <li>Racially or culturally offensive cards</li>
          <li>Cards that reference playing for ante</li>
          <li>Cards that bring stickers or attractions into the game</li>
        </ul>
